data.title: Quick breakfast
data.text: This place was great.  It was right across the street from the Doubletree.  The front room consisted of tables and chairs and the back of the shop contained a meat counter and small grocery store.  Breakfast sandwiches were made to order - egg, ham, sausage, bacon, cheese on your choice of bread.  Fresh fruit was also available.  Prices were very reasonable - $3 or $4 for a sandwich.  The place was very clean and the staff was friendly.
